column1: Modern city studio in the heart of Cologne
column2: A cozy, classy and authentic Parisian apartment from the XIXth century. Located in the most luxurious area of Paris. The view of the eiffel tower is just incredible.300m to EIFFEL TOWER - 800m to Champs Elysées - 100m to Trocadero - 50m to metro.

column1: Parisian Dream Magnificent View on Eiffel tower
column2: Central micro-studio with full equipment. Right across from Cologne's main train station and Cologne's cathedral, it's a perfect place to stay. In the immediate vicinity are the Philharmonie, Schildergasse, Cologne's Old Town and the Musical Cathedral. Countless restaurants and bars are within walking distance.
